{"tid":2150530,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警搜訂閱部門 無撿走客戶資料","createTime":"2020-08-11T03:53:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T04:09:24.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"105ca2c5337e817b82bda2a9647f3bfae66ed533","tid":2150530,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T03:53:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200811/B77IT57N2ICQEHYKQCP3WPCHGM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200811%2FB77IT57N2ICQEHYKQCP3WPCHGM%2F&d=ukYMMJnQLP7OtwhP8v88lJbpPLVkgxcsq72qYZiHPFQ%3D&h=035a466e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200811%2FB77IT57N2ICQEHYKQCP3WPCHGM%2F&h=469eee0a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200811/B77IT57N2ICQEHYKQCP3WPCHGM/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n警搜訂閱部門 無撿走客戶資料<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/ZrXl8ZRQfDS0Bv0gdC-N59JAZ0o=/190x203/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7IGB5COMSB5H46DIJUZVVEFUF4.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FZrXl8ZRQfDS0Bv0gdC-N59JAZ0o%3D%2F190x203%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7IGB5COMSB5H46DIJUZVVEFUF4.gif&h=4708e4e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方昨搜查負責《蘋果》訂閱的部門，未有取走任何文件或伺服器。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】警方昨日曾進入蘋果日報大樓三樓，搜查財務部員工的辦公桌，又取走蘋果慈善基金的日常運作文件及九部電腦，文件包括基金的金錢往來及批出計劃等資料，內有部份捐助者和受助人的資料。《蘋果》管理層表示，集團會用盡一切可行的法律途徑，向警方取回電腦及文件。<br />\n<br />\n警方亦曾搜查負責《蘋果》訂閱的部門，內有所有訂閱客戶資料，但警員最終。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n員工填問卷 答是否認識黎智英<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：堅守崗位，撐到底！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警員搜查三樓及四樓期間，有警員手持相機，未知是否拍下證物，亦有多名警員陸續推走膠箱，證物包括電腦主機及文件，膠箱上貼有不同標籤以作識別，有膠箱寫有admin dept（行政部）字樣，警方陸續將20多箱膠箱搬離蘋果大樓外。<br />\n<br />\n此外，資訊科技部等逾20名員工上班後被要求離開工作枱，由上午10。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n資訊及通訊科技部、人事部及財務部的員工均被警方要求填寫問卷，問。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n警方國家安全處高級警司李桂華昨晚會見傳媒時說，昨日搜查蘋果日報。。。。。。。。"},{"pid":"11f9a147a00cb48189176b8c91caea995cb94b53","tid":2150530,"uid":113902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T04:09:24.000Z","msg":"On 9問人識唔識肥佬黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}